    "body": "## Purpose\r\n\r\nRun deepseek-v2-lite family with TrtionMLA on Intel GPU\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n\r\nTest with XPU MOE\r\n\r\n```\r\npip install vllm_xpu_kernels@https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-xpu-kernels/releases/download/v0.1.5/vllm_xpu_kernels-0.1.5-cp38-abi3-manylinux_2_28_x86_64.whl\r\npython ../examples/basic/offline_inference/generate.py --model deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite --tensor-parallel-size 2 --enforce-eager\r\n```\r\n```\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'Hello, my name is'\r\nGenerated text: '\\nI am a 20 year old student from the Netherlands. I am'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The president of the United States is'\r\nGenerated text: ' a very powerful person. He is the leader of the most powerful country in the'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The capital of France is'\r\nGenerated text: ' Paris. The city is located on the Seine River. The city is known for'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The future of AI is'\r\nGenerated text: ' in the hands of the people\\nThe future of AI is in the hands of'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\n```\r\nor Test with TRITON MOE on xpu\r\n```\r\npython ../examples/basic/offline_inference/generate.py --model deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite --tensor-parallel-size 2 --enforce-eager --moe-backend triton\r\n```\r\n```\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'Hello, my name is'\r\nGenerated text: '\\nI am a 20 year old student from the Netherlands. I am'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The president of the United States is'\r\nGenerated text: ' a man who has been elected by the people of the United States to serve as'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The capital of France is'\r\nGenerated text: ' Paris. The city is located on the Seine River. The city is known for'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\nPrompt: 'The future of AI is'\r\nGenerated text: ' in the hands of the people\\nThe future of AI is in the hands of'\r\n--------------------------------------------------\r\n```\r\n\r\nAccuracy Test\r\n```\r\nlm_eval \\\r\n  --model vllm \\\r\n  --model_args pretrained=deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite,trust_remote_code=True,enforce_eager=True,tensor_parallel_size=2,enable_prefix_caching=False,enable_chunked_prefill=False,max_num_batched_tokens=4096,max_model_len=4096 \\\r\n  --tasks gsm8k \\\r\n  --num_fewshot 5  \r\n```\r\n>> use `enable_chunked_prefill=False`, before v0.1.4; `gather_and_maybe_dequant_cache` enabled on XPU kernels starting from v0.1.5\r\n\r\nexpected score is 41.1\r\n```\r\nvllm ({'pretrained': 'deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite', 'enforce_eager': True, 'tensor_parallel_size': 2, 'enable_prefix_caching': False, 'enable_chunked_prefill': False, 'max_num_batched_tokens': 4096, 'max_model_len': 4096}), gen_kwargs: ({}), limit: None, num_fewshot: 5, batch_size: auto\r\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\r\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\r\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3783|±  |0.0134|\r\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3745|±  |0.0133|\r\n```\r\n\r\nTRITON MOE\r\n```\r\nvllm ({'pretrained': 'deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite', 'enforce_eager': True, 'tensor_parallel_size': 2, 'enable_prefix_caching': False, 'enable_chunked_prefill': False, 'max_num_batched_tokens': 4096, 'max_model_len': 4096, 'moe_backend': 'triton'}), gen_kwargs: ({}), limit: None, num_fewshot: 5, batch_size: auto\r\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\r\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\r\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3791|±  |0.0134|\r\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3768|±  |0.0133|\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n<details>\r\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\r\n\r\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\r\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\r\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\r\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\r\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n",
